import React from 'react'
import Cards from '../components/Cards'
import { Row, Col, CardDeck } from 'react-bootstrap'
import charity from '../components/charity.png'


const HomeScreen = () => {
    return (
        <>
            
            <CardDeck >
                <Row style={{ position: 'relative', left: '15%' }} >
                    <Col sm={12} md={9} lg={6} xl={3} className="cardpad">
                        <Link to={'/stores'}>
                            <Cards src={charity} name='Find a Medicine' body='Search for any medicine that you need' />
                        </Link>
                    </Col>
                    
                </Row>
                <Row>
                    <Col>
                        <About />
                    </Col>
                </Row>


            </CardDeck >
            

        </>
    )
}
export default HomeScreen
